{"tid":359281,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(無撚恥)普捷天奴：3球才算好","createTime":"2017-08-14T11:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T16:56:31.000Z","uid":187,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b708c985e9498b86dd1a65bfc78af687776d7c99","tid":359281,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:14:48.000Z","msg":"去屆英超冠軍車路士首場比賽以2：3主場不敵般尼，令人大跌眼鏡，不過亞軍熱刺未有出事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n熱刺首場鬥紐卡素，由迪利阿里先開紀錄，然後賓戴維斯攻入2：0，助球隊氣走有舒維利領紅被逐的紐卡素全取3分。如非哈利卡尼施射中柱，熱刺可以用3：0戰果展開新球季。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n普捷天奴賽後評價道：「如果卡尼攻入3：0，相信戰果會更加理想。他們收窄防守，我們要快速移動皮球也不易，<span style=\"color: red;\">幸好那面紅牌幫助我們一把</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。在一個沒有好回憶的客場比賽，能夠全勝而回已經很好了。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=eILJjGo7kX%2BklWE%2BFO9zcv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=579dd51b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"bb0c21129e5b2f8958b61891f90e0ba01dce62ce","tid":359281,"uid":3244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d73b01326b46fc1288576448b25028606ecb7e04","tid":359281,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"屈福特 ：3分才算好"},{"pid":"420d3e925cc171990440834118a8d8c50e259bc3","tid":359281,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屈福特 ：3分才算好</blockquote><br />\n黑b :訓垃圾桶才算好"},{"pid":"7b444b7611dcc9341302bc238a8edc3928611c66","tid":359281,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"你老味射撚走我個入球大仲好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f303c3176ddbd6bfe15314f10bb191aceaf6d409","tid":359281,"uid":581,"like":0